<h1>Packet Buffer Reference</h1>

<div style="margin-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
  <a href="https://github.com/buraglio/port-buffers/issues/new?template=new_switch_addition.yml&title=%5BNew+Switch%5D%3A+" 
